{"tid":2297481,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問有無人同我一樣係路痴？！","createTime":"2020-11-23T10:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T00:49:04.000Z","uid":195944,"like":9,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8802b31d09b8e63e3e6032a865698e06b433276a","tid":2297481,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"旺角去咗百鳩幾十萬次 次次都行錯路 特別搵巴士站 試過係太子搵搵到深水埗先搵到個站<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開咗google map 唔知係咪我電話個gps廢啦 （電話費每月$60 唔知有無關係） 次次開定位同我當時位置差三條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要行左 佢個圈圈大到根本唔識郁 行咗十分鐘先知行錯方向 越行越遠 特別十字路口 我原地轉 佢個方向都唔撚識郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係商場一定當失路 放工行時代 想去廁所 直覺永遠係錯 問職員先搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當行到個條街 就永遠搵唔到間鋪頭 好似xx街1-27 我想去13a 搵到條街就永遠搵唔到間野 兜黎兜去最後又係問人先知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解我方向感咁差 有無方法解決？<br />\n利申 唔是智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85ea0e897648ece5ce48fa4953be0571e60b51b","tid":2297481,"uid":257705,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:03:20.000Z","msg":"高德啦"},{"pid":"ad81043ad657b57d14005816ad4b13aa204aeb0c","tid":2297481,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e85ea0e897648ece5ce48fa4953be0571e60b51b","tid":2297481,"uid":257705,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:03:20.000Z","msg":"高德啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"淘寶啦"},{"pid":"9e94dce3b48523d162367f8e29a1fa1772aff7d8","tid":2297481,"uid":219362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"有冇讀過地理？"},{"pid":"8f0bcb863a6e2f977e6f908b32296282e5d9a376","tid":2297481,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote"